org.gbif.crawler.strategy

Class ScientificNameRangeCrawlContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.crawler.CrawlContext
      • org.gbif.crawler.strategy.ScientificNameRangeCrawlContext

  • public class ScientificNameRangeCrawlContext
extends CrawlContext
    A context object used by ScientificNameRangeStrategy to encode lower and upper bounds for scientific name ranges. At the moment either range has to be either absent/null or a three character string.
